<blockquote>
<p>"In the Meta advertising ecosystem, creative assets are the core variable determining the success or failure of ad campaigns. According to Meta's official data, the conversion rate difference between high-quality and average creatives within the same ad set can reach 3-5x, and the ROI improvement from creative optimization is often more significant than bid strategy adjustments."</p>
