<p>In 2024, Meta platform advertising competition has intensified, and user attention fragmentation continues to deepen. According to Meta Business latest reports, advertisers need to test an average of 7-12 creative variations to find effective combinations, while top advertisers have increased their creative refresh frequency from quarterly to weekly. In response to this trend, mastering systematic creative design methodology has become an essential capability for overseas marketing teams.</p>
