<h3>4.3 Creative Lifecycle Management</h3>
<p><strong>Creative Decay Pattern:</strong></p>
<p>Meta's ad system has a "creative fatigue" mechanism. The same creative's CPA typically begins rising after impression volume reaches 15,000-20,000. Recommended management strategies:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Creative Freshness Monitoring</strong>: Daily attention to CPC, CPM, and CPA trends for core creatives</li>
<li><strong>Decay Warning Mechanism</strong>: When CPA rises 20% from peak, trigger replacement process</li>
<li><strong>Creative Inventory Reserve</strong>: Maintain 3-5 in-testing creatives and 2-3 reserve creatives per ad set</li>
<li><strong>Iteration Optimization Records</strong>: Document optimization actions and effect changes for each creative, accumulate methodology</li>
</ol>
